StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.INSERTBUILDING(pBuildingCode IN VARCHAR2, pBuildingName IN VARCHAR2,&lt;br/&gt;pBuildingLocation IN VARCHAR2, pBuildingLevel IN NUMBER, pCampusLocation IN VARCHAR2,&lt;br/&gt;pFacultyID IN NUMBER) AS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; INSERT INTO Building_table&lt;br/&gt; VALUES(Building_obj(seqBuilding.Nextval, pBuildingCode, pBuildingName, pBuildingLocation, pBuildingLevel, pCampusLocation, pFacultyID));&lt;br/&gt; COMMIT;&lt;br/&gt;END insertBuilding;
